<function>

access:   public

name: isActive

return: bool

</function>

Gets the current activity state of the cache (on or off).

* Parameters: none.

* Returns bool: True if active, false if not.

Example:

<code type="php">
$cache = Solar::factory('Solar_Cache');

// is the cache active or not?
$flag = $cache->isActive();
Solar::dump($flag);
</code>